{"tid":2267614,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頸痛加胸痛,求救","createTime":"2020-11-02T07:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T14:06:53.000Z","uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37a627af1c612c202aedb5ea64e1479accb1190f","tid":2267614,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"我胸正中間舊骨痛咗大概4個月<br />\n<br />\n而加條頸向左向右扭都好緊同好痛。<br />\n<br />\n睇急症照x光話冇事<br />\n<br />\n睇私家照ct話心臟正常<br />\n<br />\n睇跌打話我勞損但睇咗十幾次都係唔見效<br />\n<br />\n脊醫我睇咗7-9次都係冇用<br />\n<br />\n有冇清有推介？十萬個感激<br />\n<br />\n真係痛到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f5a8053d27d7b289706666fd43c0b05f49baa3","tid":2267614,"uid":357936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"平時返咩工？工時長不長？有無重複動作？<br />\n<br />\n又或者，有無做勞損度好高既運動？"},{"pid":"4e1f0039880b422932ebd2742ab5e1d2638dcde7","tid":2267614,"uid":209418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f5a8053d27d7b289706666fd43c0b05f49baa3","tid":2267614,"uid":357936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"平時返咩工？工時長不長？有無重複動作？<br />\n<br />\n又或者，有無做勞損度好高既運動？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"我平時都唔係點做運動，但有做伸展拉筋,有時返工會幫手搬下嘢，但唔重，10kg內<br />\n<br />\n,我抖氣個胸正中間雞心位會痛，頸就向上望就feel到發炎嗰種痛，扯住咗咁。同埋條頸會痛到有少少想暈"},{"pid":"6106ab852d66dbbac0f9602aea33d124c53cc91b","tid":2267614,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:09:38.000Z","msg":"照鏡照下側面睇吓有冇龜頸問題先"},{"pid":"3c871c4814b9e81da8b2be63aee695727c4c06d2","tid":2267614,"uid":34765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T08:12:38.000Z","msg":"去照ct睇下<br />\n癌症都會骨痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f8f68132dc8d6ada9cf9c2773d2fe77a5b5469","tid":2267614,"uid":209418,"like":0,